html
  include partials/head.pug
  body
    include partials/nav.pug
    .container
      .row
        .col-md-8
          h1 Giraffe Watch

          include partials/alert.pug

          h2 Sign up for a Giraffe Birth Alert!
          p Enter your email address below to be alerted when anything important happens. We promise not to spam you, this is just to help you all get back to work!

          if subscribeAlert
            .alert(role='alert' class='alert-' + subscribeAlert.type)= subscribeAlert.message

          form(method='post' action='/submit').form-subscribe
            .form-group
              input(type='email' placeholder='Enter Your Email Address' name='email' required).form-control
            .form-group
              button(type='submit').btn.btn-primary.btn-lg Submit

          h2 What is this?
          p April the Giraffe is pregnant and is expecting any day now. People are <strong>obsessed</strong>. I built this tool to subscribe people to a notification when something worth watching happens.

          p 
            strong We are not affiliated with Animal Adventure Park.

          include partials/donate.pug
          include partials/facebook.pug

        .col-md-4
          include partials/shirt.pug

      row
        .col-md-12
          include partials/ad.pug

    include partials/footer.pug